description:
Over 15 Million Users Worldwide - World Class GPS Navigation with Offline Maps & Streetview.
 
NOTE :- New Version - Before we start beating our testing team, if anyone is experiencing any app crashes please email support@navmii.com with details of your OS and which iPhone you are using. Thank you! - Navfree Team.
 
Navfree is a completely free, voice guided navigation app, with no hidden costs or charges. 
 
We use OSM map data, which is created by you and millions of other people around the world. The more you correct the better the map. As it's reliant on you, maps are occasionally incorrect, but you can get involved and use Navfree’s inbuilt feedback tool to correct this. 
 
Navfree features on-board maps, which are stored on your device. 
Therefore requires no data connection (unless of course you use the connected services).  Use Navfree abroad to avoid high roaming costs!  
• Complete voice guided navigation
•Incredibly beautiful HD maps
•Fast routing - no data connection is required!
•Missed a turn? No problem…let automatic rerouting get you back on track.
•Switch to walking mode when you’re on foot.
•Offline and Online address search.
•Simple POI search within Navfree, or use Foursquare for an extensive list.
•Navigate via Postcode, city, street or POI. What’s here?
•Upgradable Premium Content including: Traffic, Celebrity Voices, Safety Cameras
•Integrated Google street view
•+ Much, much more
 
We're always eager to hear about your experience of using Navfree - especially if something has gone wonky. If you would like help with the app or would just like to tell us what you think, please email support@navmii.com
 
 
* Some premium content not available in all countries
